d 'SVMATF': module to save a matrix to a file
d
d  svmatf  saves a matrix as a dataset. It can be saved as a
d separate dataset - or it can be added to an  existing dataset.
d This module makes use of Nicholas J. Cox' routine svmat2, which
d must be downloaded from STB-56. 
d
d KW: utilities
d KW: programming
d
d Requires: Stata version 6.0
d
d Distribution-Date: 20020914
d
d Author: Jan Brogger, University of Bergen, Norway
d Support: email jan.brogger@@med.uib.no
d
f svmatf.ado
f svmatf.hlp
